dvds.name: X-Men: Days of Future Past
dvds.summary: The X-Men send Wolverine to the past in a desperate effort to change history and prevent an event that results in doom for both humans and mutants.

dvds.name: Star Wars: The Force Awakens
dvds.summary: Three decades after the defeat of the Galactic Empire, a new threat arises. The First Order attempts to rule the galaxy and only a ragtag group of heroes can stop them, along with the help of the Resistance.

books.name: The Lord of the Rings
books.author: J. R. R. Tolkien
books.summary: We all know what it is about. No summary needed.

books.name: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire
books.author: J. K. Rowling
books.summary: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire is the fourth novel in the Harry Potter series, written by British author J. K. Rowling. It follows Harry Potter, a wizard in his fourth year at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry and the mystery surrounding the entry of Harry's name into the Triwizard Tournament, in which he is forced to compete.
